text: NEW: The House passed Democrats' revised $2.2 trillion coronavirus relief bill https://t.co/jmRQHhRJRP

name: axios
text:
The proposal would:
➡️ Provide another round of $1,200 direct payments to Americans
➡️ Restore weekly enhanced unemployment benefits to $600
➡️ Extend the small business PPP
➡️ Allocate $28 billion for a vaccine and $2 billion for more PPE
